import React from 'react'
import { Container, Placeholder } from 'semantic-ui-react'

const ContainerExampleContainer = () => (
  <Container>
    <Placeholder fluid>
    <Placeholder.Header image>
      <Placeholder.Line />
      <Placeholder.Line />
    </Placeholder.Header>
    <Placeholder.Paragraph>
      <Placeholder.Line />
      <Placeholder.Line />
      <Placeholder.Line />
    </Placeholder.Paragraph>
  </Placeholder>
  </Container>
)

export default ContainerExampleContainer
